:45:30.000Z","msg":"4年後班廢老都唔知死幾多個啦<br />\n啟晴就鉛水<br />\n德朗無鉛水㗎<br />\n有人話見到有四架旅遊車人投票<br />\n私樓同居屋好似話未入住哂 登記唔到做選民"},{"pid":"358187952df3de7ed209858ccffc9cc93462c5a4","tid":1752670,"uid":221326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"新公屋 差唔多全部都係新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde7523a622782bba0582865adf07622fcabdf34","tid":1752670,"uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"無出過來梗係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係除左公民黨條女"},{"pid":"9f483503de6ab615f75857b4cc9746311409ebd7","tid":1752670,"uid":84323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bde7523a622782bba0582865adf07622fcabdf34","tid":1752670,"uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"無出過來梗係輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係除左公民黨條女"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"勢孤力弱呀巴打<br />\n得有一班廿歲到三十既手足<br />\n其餘廿歲以下既真係用普通話傾計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老更加唔使講<br />\n娶個大陸婆加最少生一件蝗蟲"},{"pid":"cabdcbc8c61428a39be519d0593c49284446a3ed","tid":1752670,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"請條村食下TG咪知咩味道囉"},{"pid":"7666feab76d913ab2b917683e4b8c80ee4078da3","tid":1752670,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"358187952df3de7ed209858ccffc9cc93462c5a4","tid":1752670,"uid":221326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"新公屋 差唔多全部都係新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"巴打絲打 齊齊拒絕做樓奴 交表申請公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b31341f919aab2c3d9b3ab1c5459ff1f1180bb","tid":1752670,"uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p